{"tid":1365030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[727特備節目] 劉細良講啲嘢搞到我好sad！","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T16:46:52.000Z","uid":215794,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"072366217354302051f0da45bccfeff9e8c5085d","tid":1365030,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"原述摘錄：<br />\n「每一個人嘅是非，道德...𠵱個係我哋良知嘅考驗，過唔到嗰啲，以後都唔係你朋友嚟㗎喇，就算係屋企人都無計傾㗎喇...」<br />\n「呢個唔係黃／藍，對雨傘運動嘅睇法，對反送中嘅睇法，呢個係考驗你個人嘅道德良知，同埋...係咪低b嘅？」<br />\n「係咪低b嘅？最重要係呢樣嘢。如果你發現你身邊嘅朋友，都唔好話有無道德，原來咁Q低b嘅，你都唔好痴埋去，影響自己嘅智商，unfriend咗佢算」<br />\n<br />\n揀埋timestamp: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfE4DnfVj-Q&amp;t=20m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTfE4DnfVj-Q%26t%3D20m&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=5e81a6c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfE4DnfVj-Q&amp;t=20m</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係咁激進<br />\n亦覺得有啲人只係無知<br />\n但真係已經unfriend咗好多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c3afa33f1c8f7c65a36c5fc8c00bdf8b6633a7","tid":1365030,"uid":242677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"大家要睇睇"},{"pid":"ee654f6f357f041f322095d26a838ab52fced487","tid":1365030,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6d1b621b2017d744884bec33fbbd9ca6cf9d1c","tid":1365030,"uid":125145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"細良講得好好丫，話不投機半句多"},{"pid":"0ee34f833ba8802f7198b6f4756f52c80e141a1e","tid":1365030,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d6d1b621b2017d744884bec33fbbd9ca6cf9d1c","tid":1365030,"uid":125145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"細良講得好好丫，話不投機半句多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2